title.rendered: HSP Roll R Cover Series 3 Dual Cab – Jeep Gladiator Ute 2020+

content.rendered:
HSP Roll R Cover Series 3 Dual Cab – Jeep Gladiator Ute 2020+ (No Sports Bar)
Only Compatible With Tail Rail System

The HSP Roll R Series 3 for the Jeep Gladiator is the ultimate accessory
to enhance your vehicle’s potential. Which is why The HSP Roll R Cover
is Australias favorite roll top. With features such a built in LED
light, advanced water drainage and the ability to open, close and pause
the unit via a touch sensor, your mobile phone or even your factory
remote.

PLEASE NOTE: Depending on stock & availability, the current wait time for this product is
approx. 30 – 90 days from date of order.
